OL,3,CArmed murderers face life in jail
OL,4,Cafter axe attack on DPD driver
OL,6,FTwo armed men who were part of a mob
OL,7,Fthat attacked a DPD worker 'within
OL,8,Fseconds' of ambushing him in the
OL,9,Fstreet have been found guilty of
OL,10,Fmurder.
OL,12,FMehakdeep Singh, 24, and Sehajpal
OL,13,FSingh, 36, denied a single count of
OL,14,Fmurder and stood trial at Stafford
OL,15,FCrown Court.
OL,17,FOn Monday, the pair were unanimously
OL,18,Fconvicted of the charge by jurors at
OL,19,FStafford Combined Court. They now face
OL,20,Flife behind bars and will be sentenced
OL,21,Fon April 11.
