OL,3,CArmed murderers face life in jail
OL,4,Cafter axe attack on DPD driver
OL,6,FAurman Singh, from Smethwick, was part
OL,7,Fof a two-man crew delivering parcels
OL,8,Fin Shrewsbury when he was killed by
OL,9,Fmasked men.
OL,11,FThey chopped at his head with an axe
OL,12,Fand took off part of his ear.
OL,14,FAurman's killers also wielded a wooden
OL,15,Fstave, metal bar, hockey stick,
OL,16,Fshovel, knife and cricket bat during
OL,17,Ftheir 'extremely violent' attack.
