OL,3,CArmed murderers face life in jail
OL,4,Cafter axe attack on DPD driver
OL,6,FHe was sentenced to 10 years in prison
OL,7,Ffor his role in supplying Aurman's
OL,8,Fdelivery route to the group.
OL,10,FThe court was told during the three-
OL,11,Fweek trial how the attack happened in
OL,12,Fthe middle of the day on August 21,
OL,13,F2023 as Aurman made a delivery in
OL,14,FBerwick Avenue in Coton Hill.
OL,16,FHis injuries were so severe that there
OL,17,Fwas no chance of him surviving and he
OL,18,Fwas pronounced dead at the scene.
