OL,3,CArmed murderers face life in jail
OL,4,Cafter axe attack on DPD driver
OL,6,FThe suspects fled in a white Mercedes
OL,7,FBenz and grey Audi before discarding
OL,8,Fsome of the weapons, including a
OL,9,Fhockey stick and shovel, in nearby
OL,10,FHubert Way.
OL,12,FThe Mercedes, which Mehakdeep and
OL,13,FSehajpal travelled in, was later found
OL,14,Fdumped on Kynaston Road in Shrewsbury.
OL,15,FThe two men had called a taxi, which
OL,16,Ftook them to Shrewsbury Railway
OL,17,FStation where they got a train to
OL,18,FWolverhampton before fleeing abroad
OL,19,Fseveral days later.
