OL,3,CArmed murderers face life in jail
OL,4,Cafter axe attack on DPD driver
OL,6,FOfficers from West Mercia Police's
OL,7,FMajor Investigation Unit were able to
OL,8,Flocate Mehakdeep and Sehajpal in
OL,9,FAustria, and on May 20, 2024 they were
OL,10,Farrested at an address in Hohenzell.
OL,11,FThey were then later charged with
OL,12,FAurman's murder.
OL,14,FDetective Chief Inspector Mark
OL,15,FBellamy, who led the investigation,
OL,16,Fsaid: "I am pleased with today's
OL,17,Fverdict, as the attack on Aurman
OL,18,Falmost two years ago was violent and
OL,19,Fcalculated.
