OL,6,F"Sehjapal and Mekahdeep, along with
OL,7,Fsix other men carried out this attack
OL,8,Fin broad daylight on a quiet
OL,9,FShropshire street with only one
OL,10,Fintention ` to kill him.
OL,12,F"They used inside information to get
OL,13,Fhold of Aurman's delivery route, where
OL,14,Fthey lay in wait for him, before using
OL,15,Fan arsenal of weapons against him
OL,16,Fknowing he was defenceless.
