OL,6,F"Sehjapal and Mekahdeep, knowing what
OL,7,Fthey had done then fled the country in
OL,8,Fan attempt to avoid being put in front
OL,9,Fof the courts and facing the
OL,10,Fconsequences of their actions.
OL,12,F"It has been an incredibly complex
OL,13,Finvestigation, which saw us work with
OL,14,Fpolice forces across the country and
OL,15,Fabroad, which has now led to seven men
OL,16,Fbeing found guilty for their part in
OL,17,FAurman's death. I would like to thank
OL,18,Fmy team for their hard work in getting
OL,19,Fus to this point.
