OL,6,F"I hope today's verdict provides
OL,7,FAurman's family with some reassurance
OL,8,Fknowing that the men responsible for
OL,9,Fhis death have been brought to
OL,10,Fjustice."
OL,12,FHe was 'chopped in the head' with an
OL,13,Faxe, which fractured his skull and
OL,14,F'exposed' his brain, leaving onlookers
OL,15,Fhorrified.
OL,17,FThe 23-year-old was also 'clubbed'
OL,18,Fover the head with a golf club with
OL,19,Fsuch force that its head broke off and
OL,20,Fthe shaft was bent.
